    <h1>The BinaryFile Field Type</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>This&nbsp;Field Type represents and handles a binary file. It al=
so counts the number of times the file has been downloaded from the <code>c=
ontent/download</code> module.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
