</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>id</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span>Binary file identifier. This=
 ID depends on the&nbsp;</span><a href=3D"/display/TECHDOC/Binary+files+clu=
stering">IO Handler</a><span>&nbsp;that is being used. With the native, def=
ault handlers (FileSystem and Legacy), the ID is the file path, relative to=
 the binary file storage root dir (<code>var/&lt;vardir&gt;/storage/origina=
l</code> by default).</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">application/63cd472dd7819da7b75e8e=
2fee507c68.pdf</td>
</tr>
